[50.424985, "o", "\u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;2;117;113;249mTools\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243mSelect a tool to install\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m 1password                   \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Password manager developed by AgileBits Inc\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m aapt2                       \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Android Asset Packaging Tool (aapt)\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m act                         \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Run your GitHub Actions locally\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m action-validator            \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Tool to validate GitHub Action and Workflow YAML files\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m actionlint                  \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  :octocat: Static checker for GitHub Actions workflow files\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m adr-tools                   \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Command-line tools for working with Architecture Decision Records\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;247;128;226m❯\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m ag                          \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  The Silver Searcher: A code searching tool similar to ack, with a focus on speed\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m age                         \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  A simple, modern and secure encryption tool (and Go library) with small explicit keys, no config options, and UNIX-style composability\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m age-plugin-yubikey          \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  age-plugin-yubikey is a plugin for age clients like age and rage, which enables files to be encrypted to age identities stored on YubiKeys\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m agebox                      \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Age based repository file encryption gitops tool\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m aichat                      \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Use GPT-4(V), Gemini, LocalAI, Ollama and other LLMs in the terminal\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m air                         \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Live reload for Go apps\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m aks-engine                  \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  AKS Engine deploys and manages Kubernetes clusters in Azure\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m allure                      \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Allure Report is a popular open source tool for visualizing the results of a test run\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m allurectl                   \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  allurectl is the command line wrapper of Allure TestOps' API allowing you to upload the test results in real time from a build job, and managing entities on Allure TestOps side (test cases, launches, projects)\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m alp                         \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Access Log Profiler\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m amass                       \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  In-depth attack surface mapping and asset discovery\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m amazon-ecr-credential-helper\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Automatically gets credentials for Amazon ECR on docker push/docker pull\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m amazon-ecs-cli              \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  The Amazon ECS CLI enables users to run their applications on ECS/Fargate using the Docker Compose file format, quickly provision resources, push/pull images in ECR, and monitor running applications on ECS/Fargate.\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m amp                         \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  An agentic coding tool built by Sourcegraph\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m aws-amplify                 \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  The AWS Amplify CLI is a toolchain for simplifying serverless web and mobile development\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m android-sdk                 \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Android Command-line tools\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m ansible                     \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  ansible python package contains the core runtime and CLI tools, such as ansible and ansible-playbook and extra modules, plugins, and roles\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m ansible-core                \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  ansible-core python package contains the core runtime and CLI tools, such as ansible and ansible-playbook\r\n \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;252m ant                         \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;243m  Apache Ant is a Java library and command-line tool whose mission is to drive processes described in build files as targets and extension points dependent upon each other\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;2;191;135m/\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[30m\u001b[47m \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;98;98;98mesc\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;74;74;74m clear filter\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;60;60;60m • \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;98;98;98menter\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;74;74;74m confirm\r\n\u001b[0m"]
